modules.sap/ui/rta/appVariant/manageApps/webapp/:
<mvc:View
	controllerName="sap.ui.rta.appVariant.manageApps.webapp.controller.ManageApps"
	xmlns="sap.m"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout"
	xmlns:table="sap.ui.table"
	displayBlock="true">
	<App id="app">
		<pages>
			<Page id="pageTitle" enableScrolling="false" class="maaPageTitle" title="{i18n>title}">
				<content>
				    <table:Table
				    	id="Table1"
				    	rows="{/appVariants}"
				    	selectionMode="None"
				    	columnHeaderVisible="false"
				    	visibleRowCountMode="Auto"
				    	fixedRowCount="2"
				    	rowHeight="48px">

				        <table:columns>
				        	<table:Column id="appVariantType" sortProperty="id" filterProperty="id">
				                <Label text="{i18n>MAA_DIALOG_ID}"/>
			                	<table:template>
			                		<l:VerticalLayout>
				                		<Text text="{type}" wrapping="false" class="maaType" />
										<Text text="{currentStatus}" wrapping="false" class="maaCurrentStatus" />
									</l:VerticalLayout>
								</table:template>
				            </table:Column>
				        	<table:Column width="5rem" hAlign="Center">
				                <Label text="{i18n>MAA_DIALOG_ICON}" />
			                	<table:template>
									<core:Icon src="{icon}" class="sapUiListTableIconSize" />
								</table:template>
				            </table:Column>
				            <table:Column id="title">
						        <Label text="{i18n>MAA_DIALOG_TITLE}" />
					        	<table:template>
					        		<l:VerticalLayout>
										<Text text="{title}" wrapping="false" class="maaTitle" />
										<Text text="{subTitle}" wrapping="false" class="maaSubTitle" />
									</l:VerticalLayout>
								</table:template>
				            </table:Column>
				            <table:Column>
				                <Label text="{i18n>MAA_DIALOG_DESCRIPTION}"/>
			                	<table:template>
									<Text text="{description}" wrapping="true" class="maaDescription"/>
								</table:template>
				            </table:Column>
				            <table:Column id="appVariantId" sortProperty="id" filterProperty="id">
				                <Label text="{i18n>MAA_DIALOG_ID}"/>
			                	<table:template>
									<Text text="{id}" wrapping="true" />
								</table:template>
				            </table:Column>
				        </table:columns>
				    </table:Table>
				</content>
			</Page>
		</pages>
	</App>
</mvc:View>
modules.sap/ui/rta/view/RemoveElementDialog.frag:
<core:FragmentDefinition xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
	xmlns:commons="sap.ui.commons" xmlns:layout="sap.ui.layout"
	xmlns:sap.m="sap.m">
	<sap.m:Dialog class="sapUiRtaConfirmationDialog" verticalScrolling="false" title="{/titleText}" icon="{/icon}">
		<layout:VerticalLayout width="100%">
			<commons:TextView class="sapUiRtaConfirmationDialogText" text="{/messageText}" />
		</layout:VerticalLayout>
		<sap.m:beginButton>
			<sap.m:Button class="sapUiRtaConfirmationDialogRemoveButton" text="{/removeText}" press="removeField" />
		</sap.m:beginButton>
		<sap.m:endButton>
			<sap.m:Button class="sapUiRtaConfirmationDialogCancelButton" text="{/cancelText}" press="closeDialog" />
		</sap.m:endButton>
	</sap.m:Dialog>
</core:FragmentDefinition>
